      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait really?? that sounds super intense. i barely felt any pain though, it doesnt even hurt, it just feels kinda full or heavy like when you're on a plane. you sure it's an emergency? i've had ringing before and it went away by itself. maybe i should just try some ear drops or something and see how it is in the morning?",
